{
  "_comment": "Canonical Claude Code permission allowlist for the wolf-labs repo family. Source of truth: flowolf86/.github/standards/claude-settings.json; synced into each repo at .standards/claude-settings.json. Wildcarded (verb-level, prefix `:*`) so rules match regardless of arguments — the fix for 'Claude keeps re-asking for granted permissions'. Install globally into ~/.claude/settings.json for all repos at once, or union-merge into a repo's committed .claude/settings.json. See CONVENTIONS.md 'Working with Claude Code'. Deliberately excludes blanket Bash(*), curl:*, and rm:*.",
